<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Now please stop talking BS, you will lead many into death!<BR>
I say it one last time:<BR>
(1) HE CAN SEE INVIS<BR>
(2) OTHERS WILL AGRO<BR>
(3) HE IS UGLY!<BR>
Of course you won't notice that when you are way too high for this dungeon, like a level 53 necro, but an invisible level 40 character will be attacked immediatly, when he gets anywhere close to AoF. Normally this is what happens: Sudddenly you are hit for nearly 500 damage without even having seen AoF, and the whole room will agro. PERIOD. I have camped him for days and pulled him like ten or twelve times, so I think I know what I'm talking about. Have an 34+ enchanter ready when you break the spawn, we tried it several times with a level 32 enchanter and it never worked out.<BR>
<BR>
Stizok, Warrior, Veshaan</font></td></tr></table>
